description:
This retro CGI is a relaxing pixel art of Dolphins jumping and swimming in a see of black and white. Moving the mouse over the waters will cause waves. 
Change the colors of water and Sky using Wallpaper Engine controls (see screenshots).
In the original version clicking switches between white and black, and it can be found at [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1866412477]Blanc Noir[/url]
Enjoy!
title: Blanc Noir II
